fsrtool.name: fsrtool_currenttypeprice
fsrtool.structure: CREATE TABLE `fsrtool_currenttypeprice` ( `typeID` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `all_volume` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `all_avg_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `all_max_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `all_min_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `all_stddev_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `all_median_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `all_percentile_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `buy_volume` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `buy_avg_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `buy_max_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `buy_min_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `buy_stddev_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `buy_median_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `buy_percentile_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `sell_volume` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `sell_avg_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `sell_max_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `sell_min_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `sell_stddev_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `sell_median_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `sell_percentile_price` decimal(14,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00', `fetched` varchar(14) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `region` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', PRIMARY KEY (`typeID`,`region`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
